values:
I told Sammy (first one to know) that I'm bulimic yesterday... She didn't take it well. I can tell she's concerned... But, nevermind, whatever.

To whoever is reading this (hopefully someone not in school): Yeah, I stick my finger down my throat... '~'

1. Pick your birth month. 2. Italics anything that doesn't apply to you. 3. Bold the four that best apply to you. 4. Copy to your own journal, with all twelve months under a journal cut. May: Fun to be with. Secretive. Difficult to fathom and to be understood. Quiet unless excited or tensed. Takes pride in oneself. Has reputation. Easily consoled. Honest. Concerned about people's feelings. Tactful. Friendly. Approachable. Emotional temperamental and unpredictable. Moody and easily hurt. Witty and sparkly. Not revengeful. Forgiving but never forgets. Dislikes nonsensical and unnecessary things. Guides others physically and mentally. Sensitive and forms impressions carefully. Caring and loving. Treats others equally. Strong sense of sympathy. Wary and sharp. Judges people through observations. Hard-working. No difficulties in studying. Loves to be alone. Always broods about the past and the old friends. Likes to be quiet. Homely person. Waits for friends. Never looks for friends. Not aggressive unless provoked. Prone to having stomach and dieting problems. Loves to be loved. Easily hurt but takes long to recover.
For the first time in an extremely long intervle, I am very flirty. Heh, I'm going to freak out my friends today. >>;

Today was pretty unprodutive. Wrote in my Book of Shodows, played some Gunbound (gained about 10 k) then went over to my friend Jared's house to play some Halo 2. Did well, but Jared and his Halo - guruness pwn me again. His cousins were over as well, but they are bad at it so... I won. ^^

That was really it. I finally got the homosexual sexuality on Fable, which happened after I finally flirted with enough guys. Heh. Jared's cousins, even though I see them almost every week, still don't know that I'm gay. Oh well.

Well, I'm done with my book report for today. I'm on page 112, so that's progress. The stupid thing is not even due until March 23rd, but I have to read it anywho and write the report. At least the report I don't have to do until next weekend becuase I forgot to bring home the format. HeHeHe...

I just remembered that the whole school figured out that I like Brian. Stupid people creeping into my personal business. I should have known better then to blab to Scott. Stupid arrogant monkey fucker.

I dun wanna go back to school. I'm to afraid of all of the gay bashers...
Gr, this book is taking much longer then I thought. I only read 50 pages in like, 3 hours. I guess I'll be busy for a while now. Stupid Winston Churchil is taking up my time.

Alright, we have 1 week off for President's Day Vacation! Apparently we're the first county in the USA to do this. So yeah, that works out well. Gives me lots of time for me and my yaoi. *hugs yaoi* Heck, I'm just about to look at yaoi. Hehe, I love being gay. ^^

Well I just started my journal, so I hope it works out. I'm a bit optomistic about this Jounal, so we'll see how it all turns out. Basically you're here to peek into my life and spy on me, you fucking stalker. ^^ (that was a joke for the slow). Anywho...

Well, my book report book which I've been slaving over is overdue, so I have to return that soon. I'm not even finished, so I have to finish it in 2 days, and I still have 100 pages left. It doesn't make it much better for the fact that it's small print, but I suppose it isn't too bad. I try not to have to much of a negetive outlook on these things. At least I like to read, hehe.

Even thuogh I have work ahead, I'm unusually happy. Maybe it's because I've been practicing psi, but i'm not sure. I'm just all giddy today. ^^ Glee.
